WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.555
Welcome to NUSTutors, your one-stop platform
to find the most suitable tutors for your academic needs.

00:00:06.555 --> 00:00:11.197
In this video, we'll guide you through how
to use the various features of our platform.

00:00:11.197 --> 00:00:12.469
Let's get started!

00:00:12.469 --> 00:00:15.234
First, start by heading over to our website.

00:00:15.234 --> 00:00:17.330
There, you will find our homepage.

00:00:17.330 --> 00:00:23.350
If you already have an account with NUSTutors,
click the Login button on the top right to login.

00:00:23.350 --> 00:00:28.855
If you are a new user, just click on the Sign
Up Now button to sign up for a new account.

00:00:28.855 --> 00:00:40.180
Fill in your email address and password and
click Sign Up.

00:00:40.180 --> 00:00:44.590
After that, you will need to verify your email
address before you can log in.

00:00:44.590 --> 00:00:52.479
Simply click on the link sent in the email
and your email address will be verified automatically.

00:00:52.479 --> 00:01:00.106
Once your email address is verified, proceed
to login with your email address and password.

00:01:00.106 --> 00:01:03.486
Next, you will be redirected to the Onboarding
page.

00:01:03.486 --> 00:01:05.950
This is where you will set up your profile.

00:01:05.950 --> 00:01:10.580
You can add your personal details such as
a profile picture, your name, your level and

00:01:10.580 --> 00:01:20.990
course of study, and your availability.

00:01:20.990 --> 00:01:25.904
If you're offering tutoring services, do fill
up a short introduction of yourself and let

00:01:25.904 --> 00:01:30.564
us know your availability for sessions, the
subjects you wish to tutor and your hourly

00:01:30.564 --> 00:01:35.464
rate, so that prospective students can be
better informed about your capabilities.

00:01:35.464 --> 00:01:39.474
Once you're satisfied with your profile, remember
to save your details!

00:01:39.474 --> 00:01:43.850
And don’t worry, you can come back to edit
your profile at any time.

00:01:43.850 --> 00:01:49.390
After your profile has been saved, you will
then be directed to your personalized dashboard page.

00:01:49.390 --> 00:01:53.940
The dashboard page allows you to quickly see
upcoming and attended sessions.

00:01:53.940 --> 00:01:57.520
Under each tab, you will
be able to see the total number of sessions

00:01:57.520 --> 00:02:03.243
and the details of each tutoring session,
such as the date, time and location, at a glance!

00:02:03.243 --> 00:02:07.430
Moreover, it also allows you to modify and
attend sessions.

00:02:07.430 --> 00:02:10.450
For now, there aren’t any tutoring sessions
here yet.

00:02:10.450 --> 00:02:13.535
So let’s get started on booking your first
tutoring session!

00:02:13.535 --> 00:02:18.390
Simply click on the blue “Book a Tutor”
button on the dashboard or the Find Tutors

00:02:18.390 --> 00:02:20.654
tab on the Navbar to get started!

00:02:20.654 --> 00:02:23.538
You will see our list of available tutors.

00:02:23.538 --> 00:02:27.860
Simply browse through our list of tutors and
click the “View Profile” button beside

00:02:27.860 --> 00:02:32.640
the tutors whom you are interested in to find
out more about their teaching methods, hourly

00:02:32.640 --> 00:02:40.560
rate, availability and read reviews left by
previous students.

00:02:40.560 --> 00:02:45.909
You can also search for tutors by name and
or by module, and additionally sort the results

00:02:45.909 --> 00:02:52.129
to find the perfect tutor.

00:02:52.129 --> 00:02:56.590
When you've found the one that fits your requirements,
hit the "Book Tutor" button beside their name

00:02:56.590 --> 00:02:58.470
to start the booking process.

00:02:58.470 --> 00:03:02.594
Here, you'll input all the necessary details
for your tutoring session.

00:03:02.594 --> 00:03:08.008
Choose the module, date, time, and location
that best fits your schedule and needs.

00:03:08.008 --> 00:03:11.621
Once you are done, click on the “Proceed
to Checkout” button.

00:03:11.621 --> 00:03:16.193
After clicking the “Proceed to Checkout”
button, you will see a secure payment gateway

00:03:16.193 --> 00:03:20.213
provided by Stripe, a reputable third-party
payment processor.

00:03:20.213 --> 00:03:23.097
Just key in your card details and hit Proceed.

00:03:23.097 --> 00:03:35.467
When the payment is successfully completed, your session will be added automatically.

00:03:35.467 --> 00:04:00.534
Alternatively, you may also opt for a faster,
seamless checkout with PayNow.

00:04:00.534 --> 00:04:05.566
In the event that the tutor offers free tutoring
sessions, the “Proceed to Checkout” button

00:04:05.566 --> 00:04:07.963
will be replaced with a “Book Tutor” button.

00:04:07.963 --> 00:04:13.307
 Just click the “Book Tutor” button and
your session will be booked immediately, no payment needed.

00:04:13.307 --> 00:04:17.365
Go back to the Dashboard page to see your
new session!

00:04:17.365 --> 00:04:22.350
On the dashboard, the purple Download iCal
button on the upcoming sessions page allows

00:04:22.350 --> 00:04:27.260
you to download a calendar file with the details
of upcoming sessions, for easy import into

00:04:27.260 --> 00:04:44.727
your favourite calendar apps.

00:04:44.727 --> 00:04:50.100
The chat button beside each session allows
you to private message the tutor in real time,

00:04:50.100 --> 00:04:54.080
so you can let them know more about which
topics you need help in, or where to find

00:04:54.080 --> 00:05:09.125
each other, without revealing your personal
contact details.

00:05:09.125 --> 00:05:13.858
If you need to make any changes to a booking,
you can do it on the Dashboard page.

00:05:13.858 --> 00:05:18.911
Simply head over to your dashboard, locate
the specific booking you wish to modify, click

00:05:18.911 --> 00:05:21.918
the ‘Edit” button to start modifying your
session.

00:05:21.918 --> 00:05:27.871
Update the necessary details, whether it's
the date, time, or location, and save your changes.

00:05:27.871 --> 00:05:30.520
Your booking will be modified immediately.

00:05:30.520 --> 00:05:33.886
It's that simple!

00:05:33.886 --> 00:05:38.610
When the time comes for your tutoring session,
access your dashboard and locate the booking

00:05:38.610 --> 00:05:40.540
you wish to attend.

00:05:40.540 --> 00:05:44.483
Click on the "Attend" button beside the session
you wish to attend.

00:05:44.483 --> 00:05:49.100
Once you confirm your attendance, the session
will be marked as attended and moved to Attended

00:05:49.100 --> 00:05:52.699
Sessions, and the payment will be released
to the tutor.

00:05:52.699 --> 00:05:57.449
You can find a list of attended sessions under
the Attended Sessions tab on the dashboard.

00:05:57.449 --> 00:06:02.940
After attending a session, you can leave a
review for the tutor by clicking on the Review button.

00:06:02.940 --> 00:06:08.870
Then, rate your experience with the tutor
and leave a short review for the tutor, and click Submit.

00:06:08.870 --> 00:06:16.319
Your review will be reflected in the tutor’s
profile page.

00:06:16.319 --> 00:06:17.630
Need to make an edit?

00:06:17.630 --> 00:06:20.479
No worries, just submit another review!

00:06:20.479 --> 00:06:36.780
The previous review will be replaced with
the new review.

00:06:36.780 --> 00:06:41.289
From time to time, we understand that you
might want to update your availability, or

00:06:41.289 --> 00:06:44.563
even your course of study or modules you can
teach.

00:06:44.563 --> 00:06:48.110
Don’t worry, you can do so using our edit
profile feature.

00:06:48.110 --> 00:06:52.877
To get started, simply click on your profile
picture and choose "Profile Settings".

00:06:52.877 --> 00:07:06.100
Make the necessary changes to your profile
and click the Save profile button.

00:07:06.100 --> 00:07:12.810
Voilà, your profile is updated!

00:07:12.810 --> 00:07:17.580
To effortlessly stay on top of your payment
history, simply click on your profile picture

00:07:17.580 --> 00:07:19.611
and choose "Payment History."

00:07:19.611 --> 00:07:24.319
There, you can see the list that details all
the payments you have made thus far.

00:07:24.319 --> 00:07:28.259
Do note that payments for free tutoring sessions
do not show up here.

00:07:28.259 --> 00:07:32.610
If you are a tutor, you will see an additional
wallet section where you can withdraw your

00:07:32.610 --> 00:07:36.470
earnings to your bank account.

00:07:36.470 --> 00:07:41.290
When it's time to call it a day, you can logout
by clicking on your profile picture icon and

00:07:41.290 --> 00:07:47.020
selecting “logout”.

00:07:47.020 --> 00:07:52.199
To login again, just fill up the login form
with your email address and password!

00:07:52.199 --> 00:07:57.151
Once logged in, you will automatically be
redirected to the dashboard page.

00:07:57.151 --> 00:07:58.300
Forgotten your password?

00:07:58.300 --> 00:08:01.170
Don’t fret, cause we've got you covered!

00:08:01.170 --> 00:08:05.360
With just a few simple steps, you can reclaim
access to your account.

00:08:05.360 --> 00:08:10.450
To initiate the password recovery process,
click on the "Forgot Password" option on the

00:08:10.450 --> 00:08:11.580
login page.

00:08:11.580 --> 00:08:16.470
Enter the email address linked to your NUSTutors
account, and we'll send you a special email

00:08:16.470 --> 00:08:24.250
containing a unique link.

00:08:24.250 --> 00:08:29.887
Open that email, click on the provided link,
and you'll be directed to a password reset page.

00:08:29.887 --> 00:08:33.690
Here, you can choose a new password that meets
your preferences.

00:08:33.690 --> 00:08:37.730
Once you've set your new password and saved
your changes, you can proceed to the login

00:08:37.730 --> 00:08:50.463
page and log in with your new password.

00:08:50.463 --> 00:08:55.350
We hope that this video has given you a brief
overview of the features on our platform,

00:08:55.350 --> 00:08:57.700
and answered some of your burning questions.

00:08:57.700 --> 00:09:02.100
Join us and unlock your academic potential
with NUSTutors today!

